			<text use-page-width="false" push-down="false" lock-width="false">
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">Let's consider the accelerating wave which can be composed from few harmonics. In this case</p>
