				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">In the space inside the beam with uniform particle distribution across the beam, <region region-id="16641" left="352.5" top="13479" width="84.75" height="16.5" align-x="383.25" align-y="13488" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
