			<text use-page-width="false" push-down="false" lock-width="true">
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">Dimensionless growth rate (λ<sub>d</sub>=λ/ω<sub>0</sub>):</p>
			</text>
